1. *Zbog* tebe ću učiniti sve. (Because of you I will do anything.)

2. *Zbog* čega to radiš? (What are you doing *because of*?)

3. Nisam znao *zbog* čega se plašiš. (I didn't know *why* you were afraid.)

4. Ona je tu *zbog* mene. (She is here *because of* me.)

5. *Zbog* čega toliko očekujemo? (*Why* are we expecting so much?)

6. Ne razumem *zbog* čega je tako ljuta. (I don't understand *why* she's so angry.)